cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.CR, cs.DB 

The paper describes an application of deep learning with recurrent neural networks to predict the next event in a business process. This falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the evaluation of the approach on real datasets, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE) and cryptography and security (cs.CR). Additionally, the use of deep learning methods could also be relevant to databases (cs.DB) for handling large amounts of data.
